text:
Ordered soup small added enoki and peanuts with rice.

Soup consists of some pork belly meat, some meatballs, taukee, veggies and mushrooms. But sadly ribs only 2-3 which is quite little.

Service is good and food served fast.
Slightly above Average Bak Kut teh . Malaysia herbal style
Very yummy bah Kut Teh. Authentic Malaysia style! And bao ge ge himself is very friendly!
Decent claypot dishes at an affordable price. Perfect for a cold rainy day

Hi Starlight!
Happy to get my hometown bak kut teh and sesame chicken craving satisfied eventhough I cant fly back so often. Taste like homecooked!
